#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:50
msgid "Bathrooms"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:52
msgid "Gender-Neutral Bathrooms"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:54
msgid ""
"Ideally you would provide 3 types of restrooms: gender-neutral, female, "
"male."
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:55
msgid ""
"‚úÖ Ensuring your conference has easily accessible gender-neutral restrooms"
" is a simple way to help non-binary and trans individuals feel included "
"and welcome at your conference."
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:56
msgid "How to re-label bathrooms:"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:57
msgid ""
"üçé List the specific amenities and what type of restroom it is. For "
"example:"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:58
msgid ""
"\"All Gender Restroom: Facilities available in this restroom include "
"individual stall toilets, an accessible stall toilet, urinals, sinks, and"
" a changing table\" For detailed guidelines and examples of inclusive "
"restroom signage, refer to [Best Practices for All-Gender Restroom "
"Signage](https://pridefoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/All-"
"Gender-Restrooms.pdf)."
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:59
msgid ""
"Post signs in the restroom and/or on the door instructing what to do if "
"you think someone is in the \"wrong\" restroom"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:60
msgid ""
"For example: \"If you think someone's gender doesn't match the sign on "
"the door, please follow these steps: Don't worry about it, they know "
"better than you.\" (via "
"[@LGBTplusBristol](https://twitter.com/lgbtplusbristol))"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:62
msgid "Toiletries/Supplies"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:64
msgid ""
"üçé Provide tampons and pads in **all** restrooms (some people who identify"
" as male have periods and may need them)"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:65
msgid ""
"Consider using fragrance-free hand wash and reducing the use of air "
"fresheners to help those with chemical sensitivities."
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:69
msgid ""
"[Gender neutral restrooms](https://adacamp.org/adacamp-toolkit/gender-"
"neutral-restrooms/)"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:70
msgid ""
"[An easy way to tell if a tech company doesn't give a sh\\*t about "
"women](https://medium.com/@melissamcewen/an-easy-way-to-tell-if-a-tech-"
"company-doesnt-give-a-s-about-women-fb6f61249e3d)"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:71
msgid ""
"[Queerly Represent Me: Planning an Inclusive "
"Event](https://queerlyrepresent.me/resources/articles/event-"
"accessibility)"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:73
msgid "üçé Dedicated rooms"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:75
msgid ""
"The rooms should be clearly labeled to prevent accidental entry, and "
"their locations should be provided in both the print and the online "
"conference directory and maps."
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:76
msgid "Don't allow anyone (even organizers) to use the room for other purposes."
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:78
msgid "üçé Nursing &amp; Pumping Room"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:80
msgid "Ensure there is a dedicated, single-occupancy space with a locking door."
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:81
msgid "For the room to be optimally useful, these things are desired:"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:82
msgid "Locking door"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:83
msgid ""
"Comfortable chair (ideally, with arms that do not have gaps between the "
"armrest and the seat, and a set of firm cushions for positioning an "
"infant)"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:84
msgid ""
"A desk or table next to the chair (to set the pump, bottles, etc. on), no"
" more than 4 feet from the nearest electrical outlet"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:85
msgid ""
"Cleaning wipes, paper towels, and a garbage can for maintaining "
"cleanliness"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:86
msgid "Masking tape and a marker for labeling milk bottles and pump parts"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:87
msgid "Proximity to a sink for handwashing and washing of pump parts"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:88
msgid ""
"A refrigerator for storage of pumped milk (could be in the pumping room, "
"or ideally accessible outside the room but nearby)"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:89
msgid ""
"If possible, a dimmable light or a small lamp could be provided instead "
"of bright overhead lighting"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:91
msgid "üçé Gender-Neutral Bottle Feeding Room"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:93
msgid ""
"Bottle-fed babies can be fed by caregivers of any gender and also benefit"
" from a quiet, low-distraction, private space for feeding."
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:94
msgid ""
"This should be a separate, additional room (**NOT the same as the nursing"
" and pumping room**). It could accommodate multiple babies at a time and "
"be equipped with:"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:95
msgid ""
"Multiple comfortable chairs with broad armrests to facilitate bottle "
"feeding positions"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:96
msgid "A bottle warmer"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:97
msgid "Paper towels, cleaning wipes and garbage can for cleanliness"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:98
msgid "Dim lighting and in a quiet area of the conference center/venue"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:99
msgid ""
"Clearly labeled to prevent accidental entry, though a locking door is not"
" necessary"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:103
msgid ""
"[How to accommodate a breastpumping mom at your "
"event](http://miriamposner.com/blog/how-to-accommodate-a-breastpumping-"
"mom-at-your-event)"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:104
msgid ""
"[How to Set Up a Lactation Room to Support Breastfeeding at "
"Work](https://web.archive.org/web/20190717082756/https://www.verywellfamily.com"
"/lactation-room-breastfeeding-at-work-3545106)"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:106
msgid "üçé Quiet Room (also Prayer Room)"
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:108
msgid ""
"A dedicated room for people who need a break from the stimulation of "
"being surrounded by people at the conference."
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:109
msgid "No phone calls, talking/socializing, etc."
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:110
msgid "Put notifications on silent/vibrate."
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:111
msgid ""
"People whose religions require frequent prayer (such as Muslims) can make"
" use of the quiet room."
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:112
msgid "Ideal is to provide one well lit quiet room, and a second dimly lit room."
msgstr ""

#: ../DISCOVER/04_venue_selection.md:113
msgid "Consider \"quiet areas\" if a separate room is not possible."
msgstr ""

